---
// src/components/home/GuildPhilosophy.astro
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 bg-[#050505] relative overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-white/5 skew-x-12 opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    
    <div class="mb-20 border-b border-white/10 pb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-space font-bold text-white mb-6">
        The Guild Philosophy.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Technology often moves too fast for cities to catch up. We exist to bridge the gap between rapid digital innovation and stable civic infrastructure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-space font-bold text-white">
          Why "Cortex"?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-7">
          In anatomy, the cortex is the outer layer of the brain responsible for higher thought and processing. 
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-7">
          <strong>Cortex Guild</strong> acts as the digital processing layer for the city. We ingest the chaos of urban life—housing, education, information—and structure it into usable, efficient systems.
        </p>
        
        <div class="pt-8">
          <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-blue-500 pl-6 italic text-gray-300">
            "We are not just building startups; we are building the digital institutions of the future."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3">
             <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-700"></div> <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Ridwan</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">CEO & Chief Architect</p>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6">
        
        <div class="p-6 border border-white/10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-blue-400 mb-2">01 // LOCAL FIRST</div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Build for Context</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
            We don't copy Silicon Valley. We build specifically for the unique constraints and opportunities of Tier-2 African cities like Oyo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 border border-white/10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-blue-400 mb-2">02 // INSTITUTIONAL GRADE</div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">High Trust Systems</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
            Our products (UniCore, OyoTimes) handle sensitive data. We prioritize security, stability, and trust over "move fast and break things."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 border border-white/10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-blue-400 mb-2">03 // THE ECOSYSTEM PLAY</div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Interconnected Value</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
            A standalone app is a tool. A suite of apps is an operating system. Our verticals talk to each other to create a unified city experience.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>